OL,3,CCost of stamps to rise but parcel
OL,4,Cprices frozen in Guernsey
OL,6,FIt will cost 8 pence more to send a
OL,7,Fletter from Guernsey to the UK from
OL,8,FWednesday 1 April.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, a stamp for a letter posted
OL,11,Flocally will cost an additional 6
OL,12,Fpence.
OL,14,FHowever, the cost of sending parcels -
OL,15,Fboth within the Bailiwick, to the UK,
OL,16,Fand internationally - will remain
OL,17,Funchanged.
OL,19,FGuernsey Post prices from 1 April 2026:
