OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772798582
OL,3,CCost of stamps to rise but parcel
OL,4,Cprices frozen in Guernsey
OL,6,FGuernsey Post say ongoing pressures
OL,7,Fwithin their supply chain have forced
OL,8,Fthem to put up the cost of stamps -
OL,9,Fbut have absorbed some of these costs
OL,10,Fin order to keep parcel prices stable.
OL,12,FSimilar problems saw Jersey Post put
OL,13,Fup their stamp prices earlier this
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FSteve Sheridan, the company's CEO,
OL,17,Fsays the changes were necessary to
OL,18,F"ensure we can maintain a reliable and
OL,19,Fsustainable postal service for the
OL,20,Fisland".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
