OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772798582
OL,3,CCost of stamps to rise but parcel
OL,4,Cprices frozen in Guernsey
OL,6,FHowever, he adds they are "pleased to
OL,7,Fbe able to freeze all parcel rates"
OL,8,Fand are planning on introducing a
OL,9,F"competitively priced tracked (parcel)
OL,10,Fservice in early Summer" as part of
OL,11,Fthe company's attempts to support both
OL,12,F"established business and retail
OL,13,Fcustomers and our growing e-commerce
OL,14,Fcommunity".
OL,16,F"We expect this new service to be
OL,17,Fespecially helpful for businesses and
OL,18,Findividuals who sell through platforms
OL,19,Fsuch as eBay and Vinted".
